text: Loïc Chetout (born 23 September 1992) is a French former professional racing cyclist, who rode professionally between 2015 and 2019 for UCI Professional Continental team . He made his Grand Tour début at the 2016 Vuelta a España, finishing 138th overall with one top ten placing.
